urns the teamwork more efficient and effective <mark class=\"nova-legacy-e-text-highlight nova-legacy-e-text-highlight--color-yellow\">[11]</mark>. The personas created have the following characteristics [11]:  ...</div></div></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack__item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack nova-legacy-o-stack--gutter-m nova-legacy-o-stack--spacing-none nova-legacy-o-stack--show-divider nova-legacy-o-stack--no-gutter-outside\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack__item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-e-text nova-legacy-e-text--size-m nova-legacy-e-text--family-sans-serif nova-legacy-e-text--spacing-none nova-legacy-e-text--color-inherit nova-legacy-v-citation-item__context-body\">... The reason why the ICF framework was selected to support the definition of personas and scenarios, is because it gives a common language to stakeholders with different backgrounds and turns the teamwork more efficient and effective [11]. The personas created have the following characteristics <mark class=\"nova-legacy-e-text-highlight nova-legacy-e-text-highlight--color-yellow\">[11]</mark>:  ...</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-tooltip__arrow nova-legacy-c-tooltip__arrow nova-legacy-c-tooltip__arrow--body\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-tooltip__arrow-tip\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack__item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-citation-item__context-source\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item nova-legacy-v-publication-item--size-m gtm-citation-item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__body\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack--gutter-m\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack-item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-e-text nova-legacy-e-text--size-l nova-legacy-e-text--family-sans-serif nova-legacy-e-text--spacing-none nova-legacy-e-text--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-text--clamp-2 nova-legacy-v-publication-item__title\"><a class=\"nova-legacy-e-link nova-legacy-e-link--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-link--theme-bare\" href=\"publication/330266729_Personas_and_Scenarios_to_Improve_the_Development_of_an_Electronic_Social_Record_Platform\">Personas and Scenarios to Improve the Development of an Electronic Social Record Platform</a></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack-item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta-left\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-e-badge nova-legacy-e-badge--color-green nova-legacy-e-badge--display-block nova-legacy-e-badge--luminosity-high nova-legacy-e-badge--size-l nova-legacy-e-badge--theme-solid nova-legacy-e-badge--radius-m nova-legacy-v-publication-item__type\">Conference Paper</span></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta-right\"><ul class=\"nova-legacy-e-list nova-legacy-e-list--size-m nova-legacy-e-list--type-inline nova-legacy-e-list--spacing-none nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta-data\"><li class=\"nova-legacy-e-list__item nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta-data-item\"><span class=\"\">Jun 2018</span></li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack-item\"><ul class=\"nova-legacy-e-list nova-legacy-e-list--size-m nova-legacy-e-list--type-inline nova-legacy-e-list--spacing-none nova-legacy-v-publication-item__person-list\"><li class=\"nova-legacy-e-list__item\"><a class=\"nova-legacy-e-link nova-legacy-e-link--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-link--theme-bare\" href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Ana-Martins-91\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-v-person-inline-item\"><span class=\"lite-person-inline-item__image\"><picture class=\"lite-page-avatar lite-page-avatar--size-xs lite-page-avatar--radius-full\"> <img src=\"data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVR42mN89OjNfwAJDwOxHEacwgAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==\" data-src=\"https://i1.rgstatic.net/ii/profile.image/277205058899970-1443102244170_Q64/Ana-Martins-91.jpg\" class=\"lite-image\" alt=\"Ana Isabel Martins\"/></picture></span><span class=\"nova-legacy-v-person-inline-item__fullname\">Ana Isabel Martins</span></span></a></li><li class=\"nova-legacy-e-list__item\"><a class=\"nova-legacy-e-link nova-legacy-e-link--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-link--theme-bare\" href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/scientific-contributions/Alexandra-Queiros-70046400\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-v-person-inline-item\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-v-person-inline-item__fullname\">Alexandra Queir\u00f3s</span></span></a></li><li class=\"nova-legacy-e-list__item\"><a class=\"nova-legacy-e-link nova-legacy-e-link--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-link--theme-bare\" href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Nelson-Rocha-4\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-v-person-inline-item\"><span class=\"lite-person-inline-item__image\"><picture class=\"lite-page-avatar lite-page-avatar--size-xs lite-page-avatar--radius-full\"> <img src=\"data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVR42mN89OjNfwAJDwOxHEacwgAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==\" data-src=\"https://c5.rgstatic.net/m/4671872220764/images/template/default/profile/profile_default_m.jpg\" class=\"lite-image\" alt=\"Nelson Rocha\"/></picture></span><span class=\"nova-legacy-v-person-inline-item__fullname\">Nelson Rocha</span></span></a></li><li class=\"nova-legacy-e-list__item\"><a class=\"nova-legacy-e-link nova-legacy-e-link--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-link--theme-bare\" href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/scientific-contributions/Luisa-Arieira-19103814\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-v-person-inline-item\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-v-person-inline-item__fullname\">Lu\u00edsa Arieira</span></span></a></li></ul></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack-item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-e-text nova-legacy-e-text--size-m nova-legacy-e-text--family-sans-serif nova-legacy-e-text--spacing-none nova-legacy-e-text--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-text--clamp-3 nova-legacy-v-publication-item__description\"><span class=\"js-target-abstract-61a683676b7d3 lite-page-hidden\">The aging of the population is a big challenge that is imposing the Social Care to evolve towards an integrated and continued care chain, based on services of close proximity to citizens, delivered by society-centered care networks.\nConsidering the need for articulation of the care networks based on the community, the domain knowledge of professionals that work directly with the population should be considered in the development of information services that support the implementation of electronic social records.\nThis paper presents the development of personas and scenarios used to support the technological development process and for the technical specification of the information services of an electronic social record platform called the Social Cooperation for Integrated Assisted Living (SOCIAL) platform.\nThe personas and scenarios were defined based on 15 face-to-face interviews with relevant stakeholders and validated in a focus group with other nine stakeholders.\nFive personas and three scenarios were defined and are currently being used to guide the development process of the SOCIAL platform.\nBecause of the great conceptual variability found during the interviews, the relevant concepts were normalized and mapped to the personas and scenarios previously defined and a glossary was created to facilitate communication within stakeholders and development team.</span></div></div></div></div><footer class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__footer\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__footer-actions\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-pack nova-legacy-o-pack--gutter-m nova-legacy-o-pack--width-auto nova-legacy-o-pack--vertical-align-middle\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-pack__item nova-legacy-v-publication-item__footer-button-group\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-button-group nova-legacy-c-button-group--gutter-m nova-legacy-c-button-group--orientation-horizontal nova-legacy-c-button-group--width-auto nova-legacy-v-publication-item__actions\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-button-group__item\"><a class=\"nova-legacy-c-button nova-legacy-c-button--align-center nova-legacy-c-button--radius-m nova-legacy-c-button--size-s nova-legacy-c-button--color-blue nova-legacy-c-button--theme-bare nova-legacy-c-button--width-auto nova-legacy-v-publication-item__action\" href=\"publication/330266729_Personas_and_Scenarios_to_Improve_the_Development_of_an_Electronic_Social_Record_Platform\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-c-button__label\">View</span></a></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-button-group__item\"><button class=\"nova-legacy-c-button nova-legacy-c-button--align-center nova-legacy-c-button--radius-m nova-legacy-c-button--size-s nova-legacy-c-button--color-blue nova-legacy-c-button--theme-bare nova-legacy-c-button--width-auto nova-legacy-v-publication-item__action\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-c-button__label\"><span class=\" js-lite-click\" data-lite=\"{&quot;click&quot;:[{&quot;t&quot;:&quot;.js-target-abstract-61a683676b7d3&quot;,&quot;a&quot;:&quot;tc(lite-page-hidden)&quot;},{&quot;t&quot;:&quot;self&quot;,&quot;a&quot;:&quot;tc(lite-page-hidden)&quot;}]}\">Show abstract</span></span></button></div></div></div></div></div></footer></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack__item publication-citations__item publication-citations__item--redesign\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-citation-item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack nova-legacy-o-stack--gutter-m nova-legacy-o-stack--spacing-none nova-legacy-o-stack--no-gutter-outside\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack__item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-tooltip nova-legacy-c-tooltip--position-above-left nova-legacy-c-tooltip--elevation-none nova-legacy-c-tooltip--color-white nova-legacy-c-tooltip--spacing-m nova-legacy-c-tooltip--luminosity-medium nova-legacy-v-citation-item__context\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-tooltip__body\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-tooltip__body-content\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack nova-legacy-o-stack--gutter-m nova-legacy-o-stack--spacing-none nova-legacy-o-stack--show-divider nova-legacy-o-stack--no-gutter-outside\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack__item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack nova-legacy-o-stack--gutter-m nova-legacy-o-stack--spacing-none nova-legacy-o-stack--show-divider nova-legacy-o-stack--no-gutter-outside\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack__item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack nova-legacy-o-stack--gutter-m nova-legacy-o-stack--spacing-none nova-legacy-o-stack--show-divider nova-legacy-o-stack--no-gutter-outside\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack__item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-e-text nova-legacy-e-text--size-m nova-legacy-e-text--family-sans-serif nova-legacy-e-text--spacing-none nova-legacy-e-text--color-inherit nova-legacy-v-citation-item__context-body\">... AAL products and services aim to improve individual performance in carrying out activities and participating in daily life and society, which is in line with the ICF conceptual framework. Therefore, the authors argue that this framework can be used as an underlying conceptual model for the design, development and evaluation of AAL products and services <mark class=\"nova-legacy-e-text-highlight nova-legacy-e-text-highlight--color-yellow\">(Queir\u00f3s et al., 2014)</mark>.  ...</div></div></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack__item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack nova-legacy-o-stack--gutter-m nova-legacy-o-stack--spacing-none nova-legacy-o-stack--show-divider nova-legacy-o-stack--no-gutter-outside\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack__item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-e-text nova-legacy-e-text--size-m nova-legacy-e-text--family-sans-serif nova-legacy-e-text--spacing-none nova-legacy-e-text--color-inherit nova-legacy-v-citation-item__context-body\">... In particular, the personas and scenarios proposed by Cooper (2004) (the research baseline) were modified, considering the fundamental concepts of the ICF, in order to highlight end users&#x27; functioning and health conditions <mark class=\"nova-legacy-e-text-highlight nova-legacy-e-text-highlight--color-yellow\">(Queir\u00f3s et al, 2014)</mark>.  ...</div></div></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack__item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack nova-legacy-o-stack--gutter-m nova-legacy-o-stack--spacing-none nova-legacy-o-stack--show-divider nova-legacy-o-stack--no-gutter-outside\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack__item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-e-text nova-legacy-e-text--size-m nova-legacy-e-text--family-sans-serif nova-legacy-e-text--spacing-none nova-legacy-e-text--color-inherit nova-legacy-v-citation-item__context-body\">... Due to the complexity of AAL products and services, personas and scenarios are important tools to support the definition of the users&#x27; requirements as well as the functional requirements. To define personas and scenarios is crucial to consider sociodemographic data, health conditions, safety issues, basic and instrumental activities of daily living, recreational activities and hobbies, social participation, social activities, services being used, or types of access and attitudes related to the technology acceptance <mark class=\"nova-legacy-e-text-highlight nova-legacy-e-text-highlight--color-yellow\">(Queir\u00f3s et al., 2014)</mark>.  ...</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-tooltip__arrow nova-legacy-c-tooltip__arrow nova-legacy-c-tooltip__arrow--body\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-tooltip__arrow-tip\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack__item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-citation-item__context-source\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item nova-legacy-v-publication-item--size-m gtm-citation-item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__body\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack--gutter-m\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack-item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-e-text nova-legacy-e-text--size-l nova-legacy-e-text--family-sans-serif nova-legacy-e-text--spacing-none nova-legacy-e-text--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-text--clamp-2 nova-legacy-v-publication-item__title\"><a class=\"nova-legacy-e-link nova-legacy-e-link--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-link--theme-bare\" href=\"publication/317755351_Development_of_Ambient_Assisted_Living_Products_and_Services_The_Role_of_International_Classification_of_Functioning_Disability_and_Health\">Development of Ambient Assisted Living Products and Services: The Role of International Classification of Functioning, Disability, and Health</a></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack-item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta-left\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-e-badge nova-legacy-e-badge--color-green nova-legacy-e-badge--display-block nova-legacy-e-badge--luminosity-high nova-legacy-e-badge--size-l nova-legacy-e-badge--theme-solid nova-legacy-e-badge--radius-m nova-legacy-v-publication-item__type\">Chapter</span></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta-right\"><ul class=\"nova-legacy-e-list nova-legacy-e-list--size-m nova-legacy-e-list--type-inline nova-legacy-e-list--spacing-none nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta-data\"><li class=\"nova-legacy-e-list__item nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta-data-item\"><span class=\"\">Dec 2016</span></li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack-item\"><ul class=\"nova-legacy-e-list nova-legacy-e-list--size-m nova-legacy-e-list--type-inline nova-legacy-e-list--spacing-none nova-legacy-v-publication-item__person-list\"><li class=\"nova-legacy-e-list__item\"><a class=\"nova-legacy-e-link nova-legacy-e-link--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-link--theme-bare\" href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Ana-Martins-91\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-v-person-inline-item\"><span class=\"lite-person-inline-item__image\"><picture class=\"lite-page-avatar lite-page-avatar--size-xs lite-page-avatar--radius-full\"> <img src=\"data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVR42mN89OjNfwAJDwOxHEacwgAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==\" data-src=\"https://i1.rgstatic.net/ii/profile.image/277205058899970-1443102244170_Q64/Ana-Martins-91.jpg\" class=\"lite-image\" alt=\"Ana Isabel Martins\"/></picture></span><span class=\"nova-legacy-v-person-inline-item__fullname\">Ana Isabel Martins</span></span></a></li><li class=\"nova-legacy-e-list__item\"><a class=\"nova-legacy-e-link nova-legacy-e-link--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-link--theme-bare\" href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/scientific-contributions/Alexandra-Queiros-70046400\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-v-person-inline-item\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-v-person-inline-item__fullname\">Alexandra Queir\u00f3s</span></span></a></li><li class=\"nova-legacy-e-list__item\"><a class=\"nova-legacy-e-link nova-legacy-e-link--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-link--theme-bare\" href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Nelson-Rocha-4\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-v-person-inline-item\"><span class=\"lite-person-inline-item__image\"><picture class=\"lite-page-avatar lite-page-avatar--size-xs lite-page-avatar--radius-full\"> <img src=\"data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVR42mN89OjNfwAJDwOxHEacwgAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==\" data-src=\"https://c5.rgstatic.net/m/4671872220764/images/template/default/profile/profile_default_m.jpg\" class=\"lite-image\" alt=\"Nelson Rocha\"/></picture></span><span class=\"nova-legacy-v-person-inline-item__fullname\">Nelson Rocha</span></span></a></li></ul></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack-item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-e-text nova-legacy-e-text--size-m nova-legacy-e-text--family-sans-serif nova-legacy-e-text--spacing-none nova-legacy-e-text--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-text--clamp-3 nova-legacy-v-publication-item__description\"><span class=\"js-target-abstract-61a683676ba0d lite-page-hidden\">Background: the involvement of the potential end users in the development processes is a relevant issue for the acceptance of Ambient Assisted Living (AAL) products and services. Objective: this study aimed to use the conceptual framework of the International Classification of Functioning, Disability and Health (ICF) to conceptualize instruments for the different phases of the AAL development processes. Methods: personas and scenarios were modified, considering the fundamental concepts of the ICF in order to highlight end user&#x27;s functioning and health conditions, and an ICF based instrument for usability assessment was defined and validated. Results: the results of several observational studies suggest the adequacy of the ICF based instruments (personas and scenarios and usability assessment instrument). Conclusion: the present study indicates that the ICF based instruments can be useful tools for the development of Ambient Assisted Living products or services.</span></div></div></div></div><footer class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__footer\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__footer-actions\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-pack nova-legacy-o-pack--gutter-m nova-legacy-o-pack--width-auto nova-legacy-o-pack--vertical-align-middle\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-pack__item nova-legacy-v-publication-item__footer-button-group\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-button-group nova-legacy-c-button-group--gutter-m nova-legacy-c-button-group--orientation-horizontal nova-legacy-c-button-group--width-auto nova-legacy-v-publication-item__actions\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-button-group__item\"><a class=\"nova-legacy-c-button nova-legacy-c-button--align-center nova-legacy-c-button--radius-m nova-legacy-c-button--size-s nova-legacy-c-button--color-blue nova-legacy-c-button--theme-bare nova-legacy-c-button--width-auto nova-legacy-v-publication-item__action\" href=\"publication/317755351_Development_of_Ambient_Assisted_Living_Products_and_Services_The_Role_of_International_Classification_of_Functioning_Disability_and_Health\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-c-button__label\">View</span></a></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-button-group__item\"><button class=\"nova-legacy-c-button nova-legacy-c-button--align-center nova-legacy-c-button--radius-m nova-legacy-c-button--size-s nova-legacy-c-button--color-blue nova-legacy-c-button--theme-bare nova-legacy-c-button--width-auto nova-legacy-v-publication-item__action\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-c-button__label\"><span class=\" js-lite-click\" data-lite=\"{&quot;click&quot;:[{&quot;t&quot;:&quot;.js-target-abstract-61a683676ba0d&quot;,&quot;a&quot;:&quot;tc(lite-page-hidden)&quot;},{&quot;t&quot;:&quot;self&quot;,&quot;a&quot;:&quot;tc(lite-page-hidden)&quot;}]}\">Show abstract</span></span></button></div></div></div></div></div></footer></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack__item publication-citations__item publication-citations__item--redesign\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-citation-item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack nova-legacy-o-stack--gutter-m nova-legacy-o-stack--spacing-none nova-legacy-o-stack--no-gutter-outside\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack__item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-tooltip nova-legacy-c-tooltip--position-above-left nova-legacy-c-tooltip--elevation-none nova-legacy-c-tooltip--color-white nova-legacy-c-tooltip--spacing-m nova-legacy-c-tooltip--luminosity-medium nova-legacy-v-citation-item__context\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-tooltip__body\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-tooltip__body-content\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack nova-legacy-o-stack--gutter-m nova-legacy-o-stack--spacing-none nova-legacy-o-stack--show-divider nova-legacy-o-stack--no-gutter-outside\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack__item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack nova-legacy-o-stack--gutter-m nova-legacy-o-stack--spacing-none nova-legacy-o-stack--show-divider nova-legacy-o-stack--no-gutter-outside\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack__item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack nova-legacy-o-stack--gutter-m nova-legacy-o-stack--spacing-none nova-legacy-o-stack--show-divider nova-legacy-o-stack--no-gutter-outside\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack__item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-e-text nova-legacy-e-text--size-m nova-legacy-e-text--family-sans-serif nova-legacy-e-text--spacing-none nova-legacy-e-text--color-inherit nova-legacy-v-citation-item__context-body\">... Personas are fictitious characters that represent the needs and requirements of larger user community in terms of personal characteristics and goals (Eriksson, Artman &amp; Swartling, 2013). In order to describe personas, it is important to specify their characteristics in image, name, age, occupation, friends and family <mark class=\"nova-legacy-e-text-highlight nova-legacy-e-text-highlight--color-yellow\">(Queiros et al., 2015)</mark>. Customer journey map is a service design tool to demonstrate a service experience from the customer&#x27;s perspective (Sarmakari, 2018).  ...</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-tooltip__arrow nova-legacy-c-tooltip__arrow nova-legacy-c-tooltip__arrow--body\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-tooltip__arrow-tip\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack__item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-citation-item__context-source\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item nova-legacy-v-publication-item--size-m gtm-citation-item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__body\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack--gutter-m\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack-item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-e-text nova-legacy-e-text--size-l nova-legacy-e-text--family-sans-serif nova-legacy-e-text--spacing-none nova-legacy-e-text--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-text--clamp-2 nova-legacy-v-publication-item__title\"><a class=\"nova-legacy-e-link nova-legacy-e-link--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-link--theme-bare\" href=\"publication/331594714_Tourism_Service_Design_Promoting_Malaysia_Cultural_through_National_Brand_in_Kuala_Lumpur_International_Airport_KLIA\">Tourism Service Design: Promoting Malaysia Cultural through National Brand in Kuala Lumpur International Airport (KLIA)</a></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack-item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta-left\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-e-badge nova-legacy-e-badge--color-green nova-legacy-e-badge--display-block nova-legacy-e-badge--luminosity-high nova-legacy-e-badge--size-l nova-legacy-e-badge--theme-solid nova-legacy-e-badge--radius-m nova-legacy-v-publication-item__type\">Article</span></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta-left\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-e-badge nova-legacy-e-badge--color-green nova-legacy-e-badge--display-block nova-legacy-e-badge--luminosity-medium nova-legacy-e-badge--size-l nova-legacy-e-badge--theme-ghost nova-legacy-e-badge--radius-m nova-legacy-v-publication-item__fulltext\">Full-text available</span></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta-right\"><ul class=\"nova-legacy-e-list nova-legacy-e-list--size-m nova-legacy-e-list--type-inline nova-legacy-e-list--spacing-none nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta-data\"><li class=\"nova-legacy-e-list__item nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta-data-item\"><span class=\"\">Aug 2018</span></li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack-item\"><ul class=\"nova-legacy-e-list nova-legacy-e-list--size-m nova-legacy-e-list--type-inline nova-legacy-e-list--spacing-none nova-legacy-v-publication-item__person-list\"><li class=\"nova-legacy-e-list__item\"><a class=\"nova-legacy-e-link nova-legacy-e-link--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-link--theme-bare\" href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Phoon-Chi\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-v-person-inline-item\"><span class=\"lite-person-inline-item__image\"><picture class=\"lite-page-avatar lite-page-avatar--size-xs lite-page-avatar--radius-full\"> <img src=\"data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVR42mN89OjNfwAJDwOxHEacwgAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==\" data-src=\"https://i1.rgstatic.net/ii/profile.image/1045162172100609-1626197488302_Q64/Phoon-Chi.jpg\" class=\"lite-image\" alt=\"Phoon Gar Chi\"/></picture></span><span class=\"nova-legacy-v-person-inline-item__fullname\">Phoon Gar Chi</span></span></a></li><li class=\"nova-legacy-e-list__item\"><a class=\"nova-legacy-e-link nova-legacy-e-link--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-link--theme-bare\" href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Muhammad-Zaffwan-Idris\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-v-person-inline-item\"><span class=\"lite-person-inline-item__image\"><picture class=\"lite-page-avatar lite-page-avatar--size-xs lite-page-avatar--radius-full\"> <img src=\"data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVR42mN89OjNfwAJDwOxHEacwgAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==\" data-src=\"https://i1.rgstatic.net/ii/profile.image/555326487646209-1509411560112_Q64/Muhammad-Zaffwan-Idris.jpg\" class=\"lite-image\" alt=\"Muhammad Zaffwan Idris\"/></picture></span><span class=\"nova-legacy-v-person-inline-item__fullname\">Muhammad Zaffwan Idris</span></span></a></li><li class=\"nova-legacy-e-list__item\"><a class=\"nova-legacy-e-link nova-legacy-e-link--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-link--theme-bare\" href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/scientific-contributions/Syed-Osman-Syed-Yusoff-2138135765\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-v-person-inline-item\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-v-person-inline-item__fullname\">Syed Osman Syed Yusoff</span></span></a></li></ul></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack-item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-e-text nova-legacy-e-text--size-m nova-legacy-e-text--family-sans-serif nova-legacy-e-text--spacing-none nova-legacy-e-text--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-text--clamp-3 nova-legacy-v-publication-item__description\"><span class=\"js-target-abstract-61a683676b4b3 lite-page-hidden\">Airport is a great place to exhibit local values and the spirits of a country. This research relates the international patron perception of Malaysia national brand provided in Kuala Lumpur International Airport (KLIA). The aim of the research is to explore how airport can becomes potentially an immersive space that evokes the local cultural to create a sense of place for travellers. Qualitative method is used for this research and a total of nine international participants responded to this study. Data collection methods included observation, workshop and interviews. The first phase consists of gaining customers\u2019 insight from various service design tools such as persona, user journey map and user experience prototype. Followed by second phase, semi-structured interviews with a brand expert. The data were analysed using a qualitative data analysis program, NVivo12, to developed \u2018coding\u2019 process. The findings of national brand elements exist in KLIA consists of Nation\u2019s Icon; Flora, Fauna and plants; Tourism and Topography; Food; Landmark; Costume and Handicraft. Results could be used as a starting point for introducing the Malaysian culture through adding of the video playing of Malaysia attractions; Games and Art; Malaysian music; providing a taste of Malaysian food; promoting on Malaysian Borneo cultural features; providing local culture ambience; digitalization; seasonal events; constructing identity through festivals and utilized various Malaysian musical instrument in the KLIA. This will help the airport to promote Malaysia within the context of airport service environment. KLIA will become another tourists\u2019 attraction in terms of customer experience.</span></div></div></div></div><footer class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__footer\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__footer-actions\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-pack nova-legacy-o-pack--gutter-m nova-legacy-o-pack--width-auto nova-legacy-o-pack--vertical-align-middle\"><div class=\"nova-leg