nova-legacy-c-tooltip--color-white nova-legacy-c-tooltip--spacing-m nova-legacy-c-tooltip--luminosity-medium nova-legacy-v-citation-item__context\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-tooltip__body\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-tooltip__body-content\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack nova-legacy-o-stack--gutter-m nova-legacy-o-stack--spacing-none nova-legacy-o-stack--show-divider nova-legacy-o-stack--no-gutter-outside\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack__item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack nova-legacy-o-stack--gutter-m nova-legacy-o-stack--spacing-none nova-legacy-o-stack--show-divider nova-legacy-o-stack--no-gutter-outside\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack__item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack nova-legacy-o-stack--gutter-m nova-legacy-o-stack--spacing-none nova-legacy-o-stack--show-divider nova-legacy-o-stack--no-gutter-outside\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack__item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-e-text nova-legacy-e-text--size-m nova-legacy-e-text--family-sans-serif nova-legacy-e-text--spacing-none nova-legacy-e-text--color-inherit nova-legacy-v-citation-item__context-body\">... For a particular approach being proposed, one can have multiple context scenarios that depict the different situations in which it can be used and involving one or more of the Personas. It shows where and when the user can take advantage of the system, to what purposes, with whom, for how long and what is the impact of using it in that particular context <mark class=\"nova-legacy-e-text-highlight nova-legacy-e-text-highlight--color-yellow\">(Queir\u00f3s et al., 2014)</mark>. While Personas foster a shared understanding and discussion of the users and their motivations, scenarios enable a deeper insight over how the motivations of the Personas will be fulfilled through the envisaged technology (Steen, Buijs, &amp; Williams, 2014).  ...</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-tooltip__arrow nova-legacy-c-tooltip__arrow nova-legacy-c-tooltip__arrow--body\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-tooltip__arrow-tip\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack__item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-citation-item__context-source\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item nova-legacy-v-publication-item--size-m gtm-citation-item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__body\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack--gutter-m\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack-item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-e-text nova-legacy-e-text--size-l nova-legacy-e-text--family-sans-serif nova-legacy-e-text--spacing-none nova-legacy-e-text--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-text--clamp-2 nova-legacy-v-publication-item__title\"><a class=\"nova-legacy-e-link nova-legacy-e-link--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-link--theme-bare\" href=\"publication/330521315_Design_and_Development_for_Individuals_with_ASD_Fostering_Multidisciplinary_Approaches_Through_Personas\">Design and Development for Individuals with ASD: Fostering Multidisciplinary Approaches Through Personas</a></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack-item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta-left\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-e-badge nova-legacy-e-badge--color-green nova-legacy-e-badge--display-block nova-legacy-e-badge--luminosity-high nova-legacy-e-badge--size-l nova-legacy-e-badge--theme-solid nova-legacy-e-badge--radius-m nova-legacy-v-publication-item__type\">Article</span></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta-left\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-e-badge nova-legacy-e-badge--color-green nova-legacy-e-badge--display-block nova-legacy-e-badge--luminosity-medium nova-legacy-e-badge--size-l nova-legacy-e-badge--theme-ghost nova-legacy-e-badge--radius-m nova-legacy-v-publication-item__fulltext\">Full-text available</span></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta-right\"><ul class=\"nova-legacy-e-list nova-legacy-e-list--s