-v-publication-item__stack nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack--gutter-m\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack-item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-e-text nova-legacy-e-text--size-l nova-legacy-e-text--family-sans-serif nova-legacy-e-text--spacing-none nova-legacy-e-text--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-text--clamp-2 nova-legacy-v-publication-item__title\"><a class=\"nova-legacy-e-link nova-legacy-e-link--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-link--theme-bare\" href=\"publication/329620430_SmartWalk_personas_and_scenarios_definition_and_functional_requirements\">SmartWalk: personas and scenarios definition and functional requirements</a></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack-item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta-left\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-e-badge nova-legacy-e-badge--color-green nova-legacy-e-badge--display-block nova-legacy-e-badge--luminosity-high nova-legacy-e-badge--size-l nova-legacy-e-badge--theme-solid nova-legacy-e-badge--radius-m nova-legacy-v-publication-item__type\">Conference Paper</span></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta-right\"><ul class=\"nova-legacy-e-list nova-legacy-e-list--size-m nova-legacy-e-list--type-inline nova-legacy-e-list--spacing-none nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta-data\"><li class=\"nova-legacy-e-list__item nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta-data-item\"><span class=\"\">Jun 2018</span></li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack-item\"><ul class=\"nova-legacy-e-list nova-legacy-e-list--size-m nova-legacy-e-list--type-inline nova-legacy-e-list--spacing-none nova-legacy-v-publication-item__person-list\"><li class=\"nova-legacy-e-list__item\"><a class=\"nova-legacy-e-link nova-legacy-e-link--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-link--theme-bare\" href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/scientific-contributions/Alexandra-Queiros-70046400\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-v-person-inline-item\"><span c