ww.researchgate.net/profile/Nelson-Rocha-4\">Nelson Rocha</a></span></span></li></ul><div class=\"nova-legacy-e-text nova-legacy-e-text--size-s nova-legacy-e-text--family-sans-serif nova-legacy-e-text--spacing-s nova-legacy-e-text--color-grey-500 publication-recommendation-item__abstract\">Ambient Assisted Living (AAL) is an important research and development area. The acceptance of the AAL paradigm is closely related to the quality of the available systems and services, namely in terms of the user interaction. This means that usability and accessibility are crucial issues. The paper presents how the concepts of the International Classification of Functioning, Disability and Health <a class=\"nova-legacy-e-link nova-legacy-e-link--color-blue nova-legacy-e-link--theme-silent js-lite-click\" data-lite=\"{&quot;click&quot;:[{&quot;t&quot;:&quot;.js-target-61a683677062c&quot;,&quot;a&quot;:&quot;tc(lite-page-hidden)&quot;},{&quot;t&quot;:&quot;self&quot;,&quot;a&quot;:&quot;ac(lite-page-hidden)&quot;}]}\">... [Show full abstract]</a><span class=\"lite-page-hidden js-target-61a683677062c\"> (ICF) can be used to optimize the role of personas and scenarios in the development and evaluation of AAL systems and services, especially in aspects related with human functioning and health conditions.</span></div><a class=\"nova-legacy-e-link nova-legacy-e-link--color-blue nova-legacy-e-link--theme-silent publication-recommendation-item__more publication-recommendation-item__more--redesign\" href=\"publication/260364237_ICF_Inspired_Personas_to_Improve_Development_for_Usability_and_Accessibility_in_Ambient_Assisted_Living\">View full-text</a></div></div></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-grid__column nova-legacy-o-grid__column--width-6/12@m-up publication-recommendation-item__item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-card nova-legacy-c-card--spacing-m nova-legacy-c-card--elevation-none\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-card__body nova-legacy-c-card__body--spacing-inherit\"><div class=\"publ