ofile/Monica-Silveira-Maia\">M\u00f3nica Silveira-Maia</a></span></span></li><li class=\"nova-legacy-e-list__item\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-v-person-inline-item\"><span class=\"lite-person-inline-item__image\"><picture class=\"lite-page-avatar lite-page-avatar--size-xs lite-page-avatar--radius-full\"> <img src=\"data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVR42mN89OjNfwAJDwOxHEacwgAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==\" data-src=\"https://i1.rgstatic.net/ii/profile.image/431289338732547-1479838799974_Q64/Silvia-Alves-7.jpg\" class=\"lite-image\" alt=\"S\u00edlvia Alves\"/></picture></span><span class=\"nova-legacy-v-person-inline-item__fullname\"><a class=\"nova-legacy-e-link nova-legacy-e-link--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-link--theme-bare\" href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Silvia-Alves-7\">S\u00edlvia Alves</a></span></span></li></ul><a class=\"nova-legacy-e-link nova-legacy-e-link--color-blue nova-legacy-e-link--theme-silent publication-recommendation-item__more publication-recommendation-item__more--redesign\" href=\"publication/257526231_The_use_of_the_International_Classification_of_Functioning_Disability_and_Health_ICF_on_the_eligibility_process_for_special_education_services_in_Portugal_the_role_of_teacher_training\">Read more</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id=\"lite-ad-wdk8dmac1tj\" class=\"lite-page-ad lite-page-ad--has-label lite-page-ad--empty\"><div class=\"lite-page-ad__inner\"><div class=\"lite-page-ad__close\"><button class=\"nova-legacy-c-button nova-legacy-c-button--align-center nova-legacy-c-button--radius-full nova-legacy-c-button--size-xs nova-legacy-c-button--color-grey nova-legacy-c-button--theme-solid nova-legacy-c-button--width-square\" type=\"button\" id=\"lite-ad-wdk8dmac1tj-close\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-legacy-e-icon nova-legacy-e-icon--size-s nova-legacy-e-icon--theme-bare nova-legacy-e-icon--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-icon--luminosity-medium nova-legacy-c-butt