w\">[11]</mark>. The reason why the ICF framework was selected to support the definition of personas and scenarios, is because it gives a common language to stakeholders with different backgrounds and turns the teamwork more efficient and effective [11].  ...</div></div></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack__item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack nova-legacy-o-stack--gutter-m nova-legacy-o-stack--spacing-none nova-legacy-o-stack--show-divider nova-legacy-o-stack--no-gutter-outside\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack__item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-e-text nova-legacy-e-text--size-m nova-legacy-e-text--family-sans-serif nova-legacy-e-text--spacing-none nova-legacy-e-text--color-inherit nova-legacy-v-citation-item__context-body\">... Once all the data from the interviews were gathered, the personas and scenarios were developed considering the International Classification of Functioning, Disability and Heath (ICF) [15] model, in order to highlight user&#x27;s functioning and health conditions [12] [11]. The reason why the ICF framework was selected to support the definition of personas and scenarios, is because it gives a common language to stakeholders with different backgrounds and turns the teamwork more efficient and effective <mark class=\"nova-legacy-e-text-highlight nova-legacy-e-text-highlight--color-yellow\">[11]</mark>. The personas created have the following characteristics [11]:  ...</div></div></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack__item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack nova-legacy-o-stack--gutter-m nova-legacy-o-stack--spacing-none nova-legacy-o-stack--show-divider nova-legacy-o-stack--no-gutter-outside\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack__item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-e-text nova-legacy-e-text--size-m nova-legacy-e-text--family-sans-serif nova-legacy-e-text--spacing-none nova-legacy-e-text--color-inherit nova-legacy-v-citation-item__context-body\">... The reason why the ICF framework was selected to support the definition of personas and scenarios, is because it gives a common language to stakeholders with different backgrounds and turns the teamwork more efficient and effective [11]. The personas created have the following characteristics <mark class=\"nova-legacy-e-text-highlight nova-legacy-e-text-highlight--color-yellow\">[11]</mark>:  ...</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-tooltip__arrow nova-legacy-c-tooltip__arrow nova-legacy-c-tooltip__arrow--body\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-tooltip__arrow-tip\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack__item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-citation-item__context-source\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item nova-legacy-v-publication-item--size-m gtm-citation-item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__body\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack--gutter-m\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack-item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-e-text nova-legacy-e-text--size-l nova-legacy-e-text--family-sans-serif nova-legacy-e-text--spacing-none nova-legacy-e-text--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-text--clamp-2 nova-legacy-v-publication-item__title\"><a class=\"nova-legacy-e-link nova-legacy-e-link--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-link--theme-bare\" href=\"publication/330266729_Personas_and_Scenarios_to_Improve_the_Development_of_an_Electronic_Social_Record_Platform\">Personas and Scenarios to Improve the Development of an Electronic Social Record Platform</a></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack-item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta-left\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-e-badge nova-legacy-e-badge--color-green nova-legacy-e-badge--display-block nova-legacy-e-badge--luminosity-high nova-legacy-e-badge--size-l nova-legacy-e-badge--theme-solid nova-legacy-e-badge--radius-m nova-legacy-v-publication-item__type\">Conference Paper</span></div><div class=\"nova-leg